STEP 3 — CREATE / DEEPEN per HTML page
  Open the HTML file. Parse (via Read — do not launch a headless browser):
    - forms, inputs, selects, textareas → validation scenarios
    - buttons (submit, delete, cancel) → action ACs
    - tables, lists → empty-state + loading-state
    - tabs, modals, filters → state transitions
    - error / empty / "no data" slots → state_transitions bucket
    - role-gated badges or copy ("admin only", etc.) → auth error_scenario

  Cross-reference PROJECT_API.md for endpoints the page hits.
  Cross-reference _fixtures.yaml to pick the right role/credentials.

  Write YAML with this shape:

  ```yaml
  id: US-<page-basename-upper>
  role: <worker|company_manager|admin|all>   # from URL prefix (b-=worker, company-=company_manager, admin-=admin, others=all)
  feature: <one-sentence label>
