e/70 tracking-wide uppercase animate-breathe\">Finding your way home</p>\n75:             </div>\n76: \n77:         </div>\n78: \n79:         <!-- Loading Indicator -->\n80:         <div class=\"absolute -bottom-24 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2\">\n81:             <div class=\"w-12 h-1 bg-white/20 rounded-full overflow-hidden\">\n82:                 <div class=\"h-full bg-white w-1/2 rounded-full animate-[shimmer_1.5s_infinite_linear]\" style=\"transform: translateX(-100%); animation: loading 1.5s infinite ease-in-out;\"></div>\n83:             </div>\n84:         </div>\n85: \n86:     </main>\n87: \n88:     <!-- Inline animation for the loader since Tailwind arbitrary values are limited without config for keyframes -->\n89:     <style>\n90:         @keyframes loading {\n91:             0% { transform: translateX(-100%); }\n92:             50% { transform: translateX(0%); }\n93:             100% { transform: translateX(100%); }\n94:         }\n95:     </style>\n96: \n97:     <!-- Auto-redirect to home page after splash -->\n98:     <script>\n99:         setTimeout(function() {\n100:             location.href = './05-home.html';\n101:         }, 2000);\n102:     </script>\n103: \n104: </body></html>\n\n(End of file - total 104 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\"><head><meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n<title>NestFind - Splash</title>\n<script src=\"https://cdn.tailwindcss.com\"></script>\n<script src=\"https://code.iconify.design/3/3.1.0/iconify.min.js\"></script>\n<link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com\">\n<link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.gstatic.com\" crossorigin=\"\">\n<link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&amp;display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n<style>\nbody {\nfont-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;\nbackground-color: #0066CC;\n}\n/* Custom Animation Keyframes */\n@keyframes splashReveal {\n0% {\nopacity: 0;\ntransform: scale(0.95) translateY(10px);\nfilter: blur(4px);","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":".claude-project/nestfind/design/html/index.html","time":{"start":1779246041187,"end":1779246041468}},"id":"prt_e435402f1001YmTnddHXCExel1","sessionID":"ses_1bcacb067ffe1ziVpvwSLhmMv1","messageID":"msg_e4353f32f001p6uktAOQ0Wh1r1"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1779246043381,"sessionID":"ses_1bcacb067ffe1ziVpvwSLhmMv1","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_01_TmgiPm8a1sldeU0mpAW82267","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/design/html/02-login.html"},"output":"<path>/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/design/html/02-login.html</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: <!DOCTYPE html>\n2: <html lang=\"en\"><head><meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n3: <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n4: <title>NestFind - Sign In</title>\n5: <script src=\"https://cdn.tailwindcss.com\"></script>\n6: <script src=\"https://code.iconify.design/3/3.1.0/iconify.min.js\"></script>\n7: <link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com\">\n8: <link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.gstatic.com\" crossorigin=\"\">\n9: <link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&amp;display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n10: <style>\n11: body {\n12: font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;\n13: background-color: #F5F5F5;\n14: }\n15: </style></head>\n16: <body class=\"min-h-screen w-full flex items-center justify-center p-4 antialiased text-gray-900\">\n17: \n18:     <!-- Card Container -->\n19:     <div class=\"w-full max-w-[400px] bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8\">\n20:         \n21:         <!-- Header -->\n22:         <div class=\"mb-8\">\n23:             <!-- Logo -->\n24:             <div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-[#0066CC]/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-[#0066CC] mb-6 border border-[#0066CC]/20\">\n25:                 <span class=\"iconify\" data-icon=\"lucide:home\" data-width=\"24\" data-height=\"24\" style=\"stroke-width: 1.5;\"></span>\n26:             </div>\n27:             \n28:             <h2 class=\"text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-gray-900\">Welcome back</h2>\n29:             <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-500 mt-2\">Sign in to your account to continue</p>\n30:         </div>\n31: \n32:         <!-- Form -->\n33:         <form class=\"space-y-5\" onsubmit=\"event.preventDefault();\">\n34:             \n35:             <!-- Email Input -->\n36:             <div class=\"space-y-1.5\">\n37:                 <label for=\"email\" class=\"block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700\">Email address</label>\n38:                 <input type=\"email\" id=\"email\" name=\"email\" placeholder=\"name@company.com\" class=\"block w-full h-11 px-3 rounded-md border border-gray-200 bg-white text-sm text-gray-900 placeholder:text-gray-400 focus:border-[#0066CC] focus:outline-none focus:ring-4 focus:ring-[#0066CC]/10 transition-all shadow-sm\" required=\"\">\n39:             </div>\n40: \n41:             <!-- Password Input -->\n42:             <div class=\"space-y-1.5\">\n43:                 <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\">\n44:                     <label for=\"password\" class=\"block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700\">Password</label>\n45:                     <a href=\"./04-forgot-password.html\" class=\"text-sm font-medium text-[#0066CC] hover:text-[#0055aa] transition-colors\">Forgot password?</a>\n46:                 </div>\n47:                 <div class=\"relative\">\n48:                     <input type=\"password\" id=\"password\" name=\"password\" placeholder=\"Enter your password\" class=\"block w-full h-11 pl-3 pr-10 rounded-md border border-gray-200 bg-white text-sm text-gray-900 placeholder:text-gray-400 focus:border-[#0066CC] focus:outline-none focus:ring-4 focus:ring-[#0066CC]/10 transition-all shadow-sm\" required=\"\">\n49:                     \n50:                     <button type=\"button\" onclick=\"togglePassword()\" class=\"absolute inset-y-0 right-0 flex items-center pr-3 text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-600 focus:outline-none transition-colors\">\n51:                         <span class=\"iconify\" id=\"eyeIcon\" data-icon=\"lucide:eye\" data-width=\"20\" data-height=\"20\" style=\"stroke-width: 1.5;\"></span>\n52:                     </button>\n53:                 </div>\n54:             </div>\n55: \n56:             <!-- Submit Button -->\n57:             <button type=\"submit\" class=\"w-full h-11 flex items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-[#0066CC] px-4 text-sm font-medium text-white hover:bg-[#0055aa] focus:outline-none focus:ring-4 focus:ring-[#0066CC]/20 shadow-sm transition-all disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed\">\n58:                 Sign In\n59:             </button>\n60: \n61:         </form>\n62: \n63:         <!-- Footer / Divider -->\n64:         <div class=\"mt-6\">\n65:             <div class=\"relative\">\n66:                 <div class=\"absolute inset-0 flex items-center\">\n67:                     <div class=\"w-full border-t border-gray-200\"></div>\n68:                 </div>\n69:                 <div class=\"relative flex justify-center text-sm\">\n70:                     <span class=\"bg-white px-2 text-gray-500\">or</span>\n71:                 </div>\n72:             </div>\n73: \n74:             <div class=\"mt-6 text-center text-sm\">\n75:                 <span class=\"text-gray-500\">Don't have an account?</span>\n76:                 <a href=\"./03-signup.html\" class=\"font-medium text-[#0066CC] hover:text-[#0055aa] ml-1 transition-colors\">Create one</a>\n77:             </div>\n78:         </div>\n79: \n80:     </div>\n81: \n82:     <!-- Toggle Password Script -->\n83:     <script>\n84:         function togglePassword() {\n85:             const passwordInput = document.getElementById('password');\n86:             const eyeIcon = document.getElementById('eyeIcon');\n87: \n88:             if (passwordInput.type === 'password') {\n89:                 passwordInput.type = 'text';\n90:                 eyeIcon.setAttribute('data-icon', 'lucide:eye-off');\n91:             } else {\n92:                 passwordInput.type = 'password';\n93:                 eyeIcon.setAttribute('data-icon', 'lucide:eye');\n94:             }\n95:         }\n96: \n97:         // Login form handler\n98:         document.querySelector('form').addEventListener('submit', function(e) {\n99:             e.preventDefault();\n100:             const email = document.getElementById('email').value;\n101:             const password = document.getElementById('password').value;\n102:             if (email && password) {\n103:                 // Demo login - redirect to home\n104:                 if (email === 'demo@demo.com' && password === '1234') {\n105:                     location.href = './05-home.html';\n106:                 } else {\n107:                     // Any credentials work for demo\n108:                     location.href = './05-home.html';\n109:                 }\n110:             }\n111:         });\n112:     </script>\n113: \n114: \n115: </body></html>\n\n(End of file - total 115 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\"><head><meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n<title>NestFind - Sign In</title>\n<script src=\"https://cdn.tailwindcss.com\"></script>\n<script src=\"https://code.iconify.design/3/3.1.0/iconify.min.js\"></script>\n<link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com\">\n<link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.gstatic.com\" crossorigin=\"\">\n<link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&amp;display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n<style>\nbody {\nfont-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;\nbackground-color: #F5F5F5;\n}\n</style></head>\n<body class=\"min-h-screen w-full flex items-center justify-center p-4 antialiased text-gray-900\">\n\n    <!-- Card Container -->\n    <div class=\"w-full max-w-[400px] bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8\">\n        ","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":".claude-project/nestfind/design/html/02-login.html","time":{"start":1779246043102,"end":1779246043380}