;auto=format&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=64&amp;h=64&amp;q=80\" class=\"h-10 w-10 rounded-lg object-cover bg-gray-100\" alt=\"Prop\">\n377:                                             <div>\n378:                                                 <div class=\"text-sm font-medium text-gray-900\">Cozy Studio</div>\n379:                                                 <div class=\"text-xs text-gray-500\">Austin, TX</div>\n380:                                             </div>\n381:                                         </div>\n382:                                     </td>\n383:                                     <td class=\"px-6 py-4\">\n384:                                         <span class=\"inline-flex items-center px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs font-medium bg-green-100 text-green-800\">\n385:                                             Active\n386:                                         </span>\n387:                                     </td>\n388:                                     <td class=\"px-6 py-4 text-sm text-gray-500 text-right\">5 hours ago</td>\n389:                                 </tr>\n390:                             </tbody>\n391:                         </table>\n392:                     </div>\n393:                 </div>\n394: \n395:                 <!-- Recent Inquiries -->\n396:                 <div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-100 overflow-hidden\">\n397:                     <div class=\"p-6 border-b border-gray-100 flex items-center justify-between\">\n398:                         <h3 class=\"text-base font-semibold text-gray-900\">Recent Inquiries</h3>\n399:                         <a href=\"./14-admin-inquiries.html\" class=\"text-sm font-medium text-[#0066CC] hover:text-[#0055aa]\">View All</a>\n400:                     </div>\n401:                     <div class=\"overflow-x-auto\">\n402:                         <table class=\"w-full text-left\">\n403:                             <thead>\n404:                                 <tr class=\"bg-gray-50 border-b border-gray-100\">\n405:                                     <th class=\"px-6 py-3 text-xs font-semibold text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider\">Renter</th>\n406:                                     <th class=\"px-6 py-3 text-xs font-semibold text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider\">Interest</th>\n407:                                     <th class=\"px-6 py-3 text-xs font-semibold text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider text-right\">Time</th>\n408:                                 </tr>\n409:                             </thead>\n410:                             <tbody class=\"divide-y divide-gray-100\">\n411:                                 <tr>\n412:                                     <td class=\"px-6 py-4\">\n413:                                         <div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\">\n414:                                             <div class=\"h-8 w-8 rounded-full bg-blue-100 flex items-center justify-center text-[#0066CC] text-xs font-bold\">JD</div>\n415:                                             <div class=\"text-sm font-medium text-gray-900\">John Doe</div>\n416:                                         </div>\n417:                                     </td>\n418:                                     <td class=\"px-6 py-4\">\n419:                                         <div class=\"text-sm text-gray-900\">Sunny Loft</div>\n420:                                         <div class=\"text-xs text-[#0066CC]\">New Inquiry</div>\n421:                                     </td>\n422:                                     <td class=\"px-6 py-4 text-sm text-gray-500 text-right\">10m ago</td>\n423:                                 </tr>\n424:                                 <tr>\n425:                                     <td class=\"px-6 py-4\">\n426:                                         <div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\">\n427:                                             <img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1438761681033-6461ffad8d80?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&amp;auto=format&amp;fit=facearea&amp;facepad=2&amp;w=64&amp;h=64&amp;q=80\" class=\"h-8 w-8 rounded-full object-cover\" alt=\"User\">\n428:                                             <div class=\"text-sm font-medium text-gray-900\">Sarah Smith</div>\n429:                                         </div>\n430:                                     </td>\n431:                                     <td class=\"px-6 py-4\">\n432:                                         <div class=\"text-sm text-gray-900\">Modern Villa</div>\n433:                                         <div class=\"text-xs text-gray-500\">Schedule Tour</div>\n434:                                     </td>\n435:                                     <td class=\"px-6 py-4 text-sm text-gray-500 text-right\">1h ago</td>\n436:                                 </tr>\n437:                                 <tr>\n438:                                     <td class=\"px-6 py-4\">\n439:                                         <div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\">\n440:                                             <div class=\"h-8 w-8 rounded-full bg-orange-100 flex items-center justify-center text-orange-600 text-xs font-bold\">MK</div>\n441:                                             <div class=\"text-sm font-medium text-gray-900\">Mike K.</div>\n442:                                         </div>\n443:                                     </td>\n444:                                     <td class=\"px-6 py-4\">\n445:                                         <div class=\"text-sm text-gray-900\">Cozy Studio</div>\n446:                                         <div class=\"text-xs text-gray-500\">Question</div>\n447:                                     </td>\n448:                                     <td class=\"px-6 py-4 text-sm text-gray-500 text-right\">3h ago</td>\n449:                                 </tr>\n450:                             </tbody>\n451:                         </ta